-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152601t9kLQ2dFPuaDyM7J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152602TAYuQpZcksx01Cgo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152602BEkxaDjmCZqTKz7s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152602uERAJgPO5U20WXQ8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152603QMCUt8Xaof9dnxFD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121526037hMq1rdBIoCPEA3F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121526035O6lNomJxAR2CUVZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152603slrGpPiqUWLuHnZI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152604wkWoYI7bUPjQA0H9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152604PRugBSohc30k52CL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121526045TvaXj0Cktg7ewEp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152605jfZiE2r9BtVM0zxo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152605875Rg3boqS0JnCKE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152606o7kbT0MEraUx3SBF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152606wNgvWt1ou8ehTQXy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152606Ysd156w4bEXNumUP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152607Og73poScilrUe5zk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Oscar de la renta 2019 春夏系列：</strong></p><p>设计师 Laura Kim 和 Fernando Garcia 将其称作一个“游牧感十足”（nomadic）的系列。两人于今年春季开始构思，各自去印度、意大利、科莫湖、马拉喀什、克罗地亚。整个系列在飘逸轻松的廓型外又增加了许多带有异域风情的装饰性元素，比如流苏和刺绣。由于发布会举行当天是 9 月 11 日，shownote 上留了白，美国国旗上印了一行小字：“今天我们缅怀 9.11 中逝去的至亲，并向重建这座城市的人致以敬意。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152926sKkodGlDIwhaS8zV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121529269wdp256KLBZbVC7F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152926GeyxqSdmViA2zscP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152927PYe6DT7kMW9u3pHQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152927A1Ncp7mBGIJFWkVh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152927sOH1TS3o6Nv4YXzn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018091215292859fl8OZQGYsCzuA0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912152928nDHT0hcXxBjYlodA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-f