<p><strong>Coach 1941 2019 春夏系列：</strong></p><p>无论是秀场布置还是服装的色调，Coach 创意总监&nbsp;Stuart Vevers 的新系列都让人联想起美国新墨西哥州。皮衣、纱裙、印花卫衣和 T 恤的混搭制造出又朋克又浪漫的氛围。《女装日报》认为这个系列“用当代视角诠释了 80 年代兴起的新浪漫主义风潮”。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153104g4oSmwNP1CbZ93OQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121531047d0T5I6lNmygDPcJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153105RvruLweVtIFyikGB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153105fBTGWDqIJmQ6v2ox.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153106EaDjHAV6Rw48Licp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153106ZhxaKs9iVIAWcPzt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153107O1blupD7W8VY2UTx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153107SWiGvr3b4xfU0jap.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153107ZYA8wKJQCtTnFGI5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153107l5sINnchBYZCJV8j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153108uia7kJgALTRV4CNK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153108FxA7yoBICbLpZnm0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><fi