mg src=\"img/uploads/20180912153118d8OzZab47nL9SwCA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153119QiypAcFBVCPbzLjE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153118gNRbcFxPCk8hwLZ6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153119VU5QhMOtWxT4zHjs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153119fKwcLORDiaXGUd1W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153120NLKtQopq4PD3JeyX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153120lFu2q7v4OkjzWw1I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121531203qQOxIGbMRYk1Xic.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153120xpRkiL4vVMFqCsN1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153121r16dHVhmFUtc8fjK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153121WuUFvHfO9kXoacEV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153122UtlCvoNZe3Oi9rWQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121531216yMNrVR79tBTKaq3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Rodarte 2019 春夏系列：</strong></p><p>这场秀是在纽约东村的大理石公墓里举行的，天气阴沉，还下着小雨。但 Rodarte 姐妹的新系列却充满热情，薄纱、蕾丝、绸缎、蝴蝶结、刺绣等充满女性气息的元素堆砌到一起，构成一群似乎在现实和幻境间游荡的生物。</p><p>“美国时尚太强调商业性了，我们认为这种狭隘令人窒息。”这场秀就是她们的一次抗议。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809121533242zYIBwy6JQrp07fS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153322rYuVXJaqMZS76siQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153318ErCTL637RoYKXpnZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153318dpkLBqDwCSGY0QsU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153322YtQKZDzTLxbrOco5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153323G86Rei75sn9PLZ1y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153325r02hvnzWV1ecgYoq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153325RCvsrXfLngVAOjGd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153326fTki4cYmCnjXK39U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153327PkmBtnOYuX9dv2Th.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153327BguTlNz2t7k1o8Sw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153327JmY3zF8AhbUCpd1j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180912153328hpGNBFUjnPLsEez4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.50073